{"id":180961,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/global-voices-沙特阿拉伯：人权斗士受审/","date":"2011-09-22T23:00:42Z","modified":"2011-09-22T23:00:42Z","title":"Global Voices | 沙特阿拉伯：人权斗士受审","content":"<p><p>2011年9月10日星期六，沙特阿拉伯人权斗士Waleed Abu Alkhair（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair\">@abualkhair</a>）因“侮辱司法”而面对吉达的国家法庭。沙乌地推特用户讨论Abu Alkhair的案件时，使用<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23abualkhair\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23abualkhair\">#abualkhair</a>和<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23wAbuAlkhair\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23wAbuAlkhair\">#wAbuAlkhair</a>等标签表示支持。有些人批评当局对待行动主义者的方式，因为当局把Abu Alkhair形容为背叛沙乌地王国的“外国特务”。</p>\n<p>后来发现这位沙乌地维权斗士不仅面对侮辱司法的指控，还有要求君主立宪和其它的指控。法官拒绝给Abu Alkhair一份指控内容的文件。在接下来的推特讯息中，Abu Alkhair提到他所面对的指控，以及第一次开庭时发生的事：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://abdofares.blogspot.com/2009/07/blog-post_12.html\"><img title=\"Picture of Saudi Activist Waleed Abu Alkhair taken from the blog of Abdulrahman Fares\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Waleed-Abu-Alkhair-293x300.jpg\" alt=\"Picture of Saudi Activist Waleed Abu Alkhair taken from the blog of Abdulrahman Fares\" width=\"205\" height=\"210\" /></a></p>\n<p>沙乌地维权斗士Waleed Abu Alkhair的照片，取自Abdulrahman Fares博客</p>\n</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair/status/112794210440200192\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair/status/112794210440200192\">@abualkhair</a>：我见了法官助理，他念出对我的指控，包括侮辱司法和为其工作的人，还有联系外国机构。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair/status/112795207011020801\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair/status/112795207011020801\">@abualkhair</a>：其他指控有，要求君主立宪以及在媒体上败坏国家的名声。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair/status/112796237660565504\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair/status/112796237660565504\">@abualkhair</a>：还有另一项指控是鼓励我妻子Samar Badawi反抗当局。法官拒绝给我一份指控的副本。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair/status/112797281606049793\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair/status/112797281606049793\">@abualkhair</a>：他[法官]也拒绝告诉我下次审讯是何时，只叫我等他们打电话通知我这方面的消息。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair/status/112800157476716545\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair/status/112800157476716545\">@abualkhair</a>：案件是由Abdulmajid Al Shuwaihi法官审理，但检控官没有出席，而我现在要回家了，哈哈哈</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abualkhair/status/112810666938732545\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abualkhair/status/112810666938732545\">@abualkhair</a>：我忘了补充的是，其中一项指控是鼓励人民违反国家公共秩序。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>沙乌地的推特用户Mansour johny（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/Alasbani1\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/Alasbani1\">@Alasbani1</a>）评论这场审判：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/Alasbani1/status/112956879235325952\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/Alasbani1/status/112956879235325952\">@Alasbani1</a>：只有在沙乌地你会因表达意见而受到审判，就如同你对某人犯了罪一样。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>另一位沙乌地的推特用户（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/MyyVoicee\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/MyyVoicee\">@MyyVoicee</a>）以言论自由的角度看这件事：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/MyyVoicee/status/112937559528718337\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/MyyVoicee/status/112937559528718337\">@MyyVoicee</a>：我们都知道Abu Alkhair的审判是虚假的，其真正目的是压抑自由。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Mosfer Alwadee（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/MosferAlwadee\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/MosferAlwadee\">@MosferAlwadee</a>）于推特上讥讽此次审判：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/MosferAlwadee/status/112934826872545280\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/MosferAlwadee/status/112934826872545280\">@MosferAlwadee</a>：要求君主立宪是一项重罪，要求司法改革是一种侮辱，捍卫人民的权利是违背国家的行为。那还有什么好笑的？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>沙乌地民权与政权协会（Saudi Civil and Political Rights Association）的共同创办人兼主席Mohammad Al-Qahtani（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/MFQahtani\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/MFQahtani\">@MFQahtani</a>）认为这场审判是一种压制：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/MFQahtani/status/112811676218306561\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/MFQahtani/status/112811676218306561\">@MFQahtani</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23abualkhair\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23abualkhair\">#abualkhair</a>的法庭审判披露了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23saudi\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23saudi\">#沙乌地</a>的司法制度有严重的差别地对待，而且非常政治化！法院已成为另一种压制的工具吗？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>不过沙乌地匿名者（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/Saamaa2\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/Saamaa2\">@Saamaa2</a>）站在反对Abu Alkhair的阵营：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/Saamaa2/status/113031354622558209\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/Saamaa2/status/113031354622558209\">@Saamaa2</a>：除了像他自己一样的傀儡和缺乏诚信的组织，无人为#abualkhair #wAbuAlkhair辩护，这是多么地荒谬。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Abdulaziz（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abumjd\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abumjd\">@abumjd</a>）认为Abu Alkhair 是位“外国特务”：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/abumjd/status/112989258779852800\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/abumjd/status/112989258779852800\">@abumjd</a>：当司法制度为了一位特务而受到攻击时，以笑脸对待吧，因为你在沙乌地。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>另一位沙乌地匿名者（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/SAHER1010\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/SAHER1010\">@SAHER1010</a>）写道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/SAHER1010/status/112981893036781568\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/SAHER1010/status/112981893036781568\">@SAHER1010</a>：Waleed Abu Alkhair以为，身为人权观察组织的“特务”能让自己在审判中获得国际保护。你没有时间了，试试另一个把戏吧。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mona-kareem/\" title=\"文章导读 Mona Kareem\">Mona Kareem</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/tina/\" title=\"文章导读 Tina Campling\">Tina Campling</a> </span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/09/12/saudi-arabia-human-rights-activist-on-trial/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/09/23/9857/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;desc=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;text=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;title=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;title=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;title=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1\" title=\"delicious\"><span>delicious</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.instapaper.com/edit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F23%2F9857%2F&#038;title=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E6%96%97%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A1\" title=\"Instapaper\"><span>Instapaper</span></a></span>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[9050]}